Package assign02

package assign02
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    CurrentPatient
    This class represents a UHealth patient who has a unique UHealthID, a first name, a last name, a physician, and a last visit date.
    CurrentPatientGeneric<Type>
    This class represents a UHealth patient who has a unique UHealthID, a first name, a last name, a physician, and a last visit date.
    Facility
    This class represents a record of patients that have visited a UHealth facility.
    FacilityGeneric<Type>
    This class represents a record of patients that have visited a UHealth facility.
    FacilityGenericTester
    This class contains tests for FacilityGeneric.
    FacilityTester
    This class contains tests for Facility.
    OrderByDate<Type>
    Comparator that defines an ordering among current patients using the date of their last visit and their uHealthIDs.
    OrderByName<Type>
    Comparator that defines an ordering among current patients using their first name, last name, and uHealthIDs.
    OrderByUHealthID<Type>
    Comparator that defines an ordering among current patients using their uHealthIDs.
    Patient
    This class represents a UHealth patient who has a unique UHealthID, a first name, and a last name.
    UHealthID
    This class represents a unique UHealthID, which has a four letter prefix and four number suffix, such as ABCD-0123.
